2026-02-26 16:42:15 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@id='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT b1."Id", b1."Content", b1."CorrectAnswerId", b1."Image", b0."Id", b0."AnswerIndex", b0."BaseQuestionId", b0."Content"
FROM (
    SELECT b."Id", b."Content", b."CorrectAnswerId", b."Image"
    FROM "BaseQuestions" AS b
    WHERE b."Id" = @id
    LIMIT 1
) AS b1
